{"tid":2055826,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中資保險公司挾港人資金當提款機 苦主投保800萬焗供","createTime":"2020-06-08T08:51:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T17:20:44.000Z","uid":53003,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8036f1f5f3484b10f07631ecd31c912f1064bb73","tid":2055826,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:51:29.000Z","msg":"內地上市民企泰禾集團近月陷入財務危機，旗下保管香港人保險資金的泰禾人壽更險成提款機。港人Calvin（化名）過去1年經大新銀行投保6張泰壽保單、涉資800萬港元，坦言當初投保全因信賴香港銀行及金融制度，豈料背後中資母企竟陷入財困，此刻退保僅可取回4成已繳保費，倒蝕230萬元，揚言以後不沾手中資金融產品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200608/7Q2GE6AS6FEX745VZXDQOKKXRQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200608%2F7Q2GE6AS6FEX745VZXDQOKKXRQ%2F&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KZODbC9uMYpCHTvDpi7yeoo%3D&h=afbbdd5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200608%2F7Q2GE6AS6FEX745VZXDQOKKXRQ%2F&h=57812c32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200608/7Q2GE6AS6FEX745VZXDQOKKXRQ/</a>"},{"pid":"412ac4ecff17594c28bd7b7335aedd1b39010957","tid":2055826,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:53:07.000Z","msg":"又係泰禾人壽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0673eef1eef88f627a69d22bde7d4dd7738961a4","tid":2055826,"uid":18395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:54:30.000Z","msg":"古巨基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53bf3856e64964a42719d38644d9ee01cfd6cc6c","tid":2055826,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:55:49.000Z","msg":"抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/05/TzJ2Ao.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F05%2FTzJ2Ao.gif&h=0eb51075&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43ac1f9eaedc0ac1adf16840dfe58e4e5de8559c","tid":2055826,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:55:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2017年11月24日，大新人壽保險有限公司正式改名為泰禾人壽保險有限公司。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當年2017年已經變咗中資<br />\n<br />\n咁你2019年, 叫你杯葛中資, 你又唔聽<br />\n仲去幫趁800萬<br />\n咁係咪自己抵撚死呢？"},{"pid":"a1d9d909f3782153c59ecfcd76df94c5bd526eb3","tid":2055826,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53bf3856e64964a42719d38644d9ee01cfd6cc6c","tid":2055826,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:55:49.000Z","msg":"抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/05/TzJ2Ao.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F05%2FTzJ2Ao.gif&h=0eb51075&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:56:12.000Z","msg":"幫趁中資抵撚死"},{"pid":"f6d5da657312a30f26eb5e2cd1f545c4c9e047e1","tid":2055826,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad12e7a24767549d81e8ba498cc8734e72bd9efe","tid":2055826,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:57:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/財經快訊/473127/泰禾集團終止向母企-收購泰禾人壽全部股權\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A%2F473127%2F%E6%B3%B0%E7%A6%BE%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98%E7%B5%82%E6%AD%A2%E5%90%91%E6%AF%8D%E4%BC%81-%E6%94%B6%E8%B3%BC%E6%B3%B0%E7%A6%BE%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%BD%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E8%82%A1%E6%AC%8A&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KZODbC9uMYpCHTvDpi7yeoo%3D&h=b0a986da\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/財經快訊/473127/泰禾集團終止向母企-收購泰禾人壽全部股權</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">泰禾集團終止向母企 收購泰禾人壽全部股權</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2020-05-14 18:20<br />\n最後更新日期：2020-05-14 18:20<br />\n內地房地產開發商、深圳上市的泰禾集團表示，終止收購母企泰禾投資持有的泰禾人壽全部股權。<br />\n<br />\n公告指出，因本次交易尚需經香港保險業監管局、澳門金融管理局等有關部門審批通過，以及公司董事會、股東大會審議批准後方可繼續推進。鑒於目前公司被法院列為被執行人、存在債務逾期事項，以及香港地區目前的經濟局勢等相關原因，相關部門事前審批環節存在重大不確定性。公司與泰禾投資經審慎研究相關事項，認為雙方無法在短時間內就目前該交易受到的影響形成明確可行的解決方案，因此決定終止本次重組事項。<br />\n<br />\n泰禾集團於4月底在深交所發出公告，指有意透過發行新股向泰禾投資收購泰禾人壽，惟集團近日傳出在內地面對資金困難，最新公布稱，收到相關通知，得知公司被列為被執行人。"},{"pid":"f72db5e8d6d84a52325db260c70afe7ac53d3b65","tid":2055826,"uid":137159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:58:00.000Z","msg":"依間福建佬公司黎架，佢夾左香港客啲保費去借俾自己母公母。<br />\n<br />\n不過，買保險咁多選擇都走去揀支那野，係抵鳩死"},{"pid":"3e6a367b7546998031a7ae299b6e01d61c451f8c","tid":2055826,"uid":224533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:59:08.000Z","msg":"最好多啲藍絲中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf0dfa8666fbaaaac1908e17fbce3a00e3fddd5","tid":2055826,"uid":282359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:59:54.000Z","msg":"嘻嘻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff5de0f4d2f480edc940c09cedc99ea29be23cc","tid":2055826,"uid":282897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f72db5e8d6d84a52325db260c70afe7ac53d3b65","tid":2055826,"uid":137159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:58:00.000Z","msg":"依間福建佬公司黎架，佢夾左香港客啲保費去借俾自己母公母。<br />\n<br />\n不過，買保險咁多選擇都走去揀支那野，係抵鳩死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T09:00:10.000Z","msg":"支爆緊仲放$去由去中國公司....."},{"pid":"1baf7ca83aeb6a46eddbbe504473780939325480","tid":2055826,"uid":41960,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,